ğŸš€ Quick Start (Run Locally)
Step 1: Clone & Setup
bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/razilchristian/stock-market-prediction.git
cd stock-market-prediction

# Navigate to the js directory (where app.py is located)
cd js

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
Step 2: Run the Server
bash
python app.py
Step 3: Access the System
Local Web Interface: http://localhost:8080

API Endpoint: http://localhost:8080/api/predict

Health Check: http://localhost:8080/api/health

